    {
      "id": "chat-step7-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1896,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 128,
      "text": "7  PART RENDERER PIPELINE (client — per message part)\nText parts:\n  1. parseChoices(text) → extract ---choices--- / ---/choices--- blocks from raw text\n  2. rubyToHtml(text) → convert {kanji|reading} annotations to <ruby><rb>kanji</rb><rt>reading</rt></ruby>\n  3. <Markdown rehypePlugins={[rehypeRaw]}> → renders HTML with furigana, blockquotes, italics\n  4. <ChoiceButtons> rendered below markdown if choice blocks were found\nTool parts: type starts with 'tool-' → return null (hidden from visible render)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
