      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "7  PART RENDERER PIPELINE (client — per message part)\nText parts:\n  1. parseChoices(text) → extract ---choices--- / ---/choices--- blocks from raw text\n  2. rubyToHtml(text) → convert {kanji|reading} annotations to <ruby><rb>kanji</rb><rt>reading</rt></ruby>\n  3. <Markdown rehypePlugins={[rehypeRaw]}> → renders HTML with furigana, blockquotes, italics\n  4. <ChoiceButtons> rendered below markdown if choice blocks were found\nTool parts: type starts with 'tool-' → return null (hidden from visible render)",
